### AdwPreferencesPage / AdwPreferencesGroup
Settings UI.

```tsx
<AdwPreferencesPage title="Settings">
    <AdwPreferencesGroup title="Appearance" description="Customize look">
        <AdwSwitchRow title="Dark Mode" active={dark} onActivated={() => setDark(!dark)} />
